ending steam project demand.","It was received letter from AMBU regarding the fresh water consumption in Q1-2026. The request for payment will be submitted in OA system.","Hot water with Surfactant and Viscosity Reducer, Huff & Puff.","6002/M – to recover 764m3; FDT 245m; W/C 90%","5577/G4: to recover 1066m3; FDT 150m; Net 1.9m3/d","5284/G4: to recover 1733m3; FDT 1176m","5836/D3L: to recover 31.6m3; FDT 228m; Net 3.4m3/d","5614/G6: to recover 13819m3; FDT 708m","CTF Gas Flotation Unit:","Pad H:","Diluent usage 9 m3/day.","244 m3 diluent was supplied.","Sat#3:","Diluent usage 18 m3/day.","Pad D:","Diluent usage 12 m3/day.","Water disposal:","Push water line (dry gas line) from sat#3 to Kallmi, out of service.","Repairing Kallmi bridge box.","G-31-A Tank#4 , opened and cleaned.","I-30-A 1854 shut in, high casing pressure.","133 m3 skim/slop removed from water tanks in disposal pads.","Chemical","Stopped trial @ O-24-B BHH-1040, not good results on dropping water cut.","Ongoing trial ,O-34-B with new demulsifier BHH 1039 & from Hai Long company."],"tables":[{"rows":[["","Ave this week ( May 10th, m3/d)","Ave this week ( May 10th, m3/d)","Ave this week ( May 10th, m3/d)","Cum production in YTD,m3","Cum production in YTD,m3","Cum production in YTD,m3"],["","Budget","Actual","Actual -Budget","Budget","Actual","Actual - Budget"],["Existing well","919","900","-19","115,111","112,204","-2907"],["New non-thermal well","0","0","0","0","0","0"],["Polymer conversion","0","0","0","0","0","0"],["Reactivation+Stimulation","0","0","0","0","0","0"],["Thermal","124","95","-29","16,316","14,712","-1604"],["Total","1,043","995","-48","131,427","126,916","-4511"]]},{"rows":[["","","Oil Production m3/d","Oil Production m3/d","Variance"],["","","Last Week","This Week","+/- (m3/d)"],["Central","PF&WF","236.6","239.4","2.8"],["North","PF","53.4","54.7","1.2"],["South","PF","89.6","92.4","2.8"],["EOR TOTAL","PF&WF","379.7","386.5","6.8"]]},{"rows":[["ID","Brief Description"]]},{"rows":[["ID"