. Water supply of boiler# 1 continue normal","Preparations for the high temperatures of the season are ongoing. Ventilation and sun protection. Prepared the 1st sunshade for the WSW flowmeters. The others will be prepared by our contractor.","Looking for simple but safe options for converting production wells to polymer injectors based on the experience and the data of recent years.","Hot water with Surfactant and Viscosity Reducer, Huff & Puff.","6002/M – to recover 563.5m3; FDT 102m; W/C 75%","5577/G4: to recover 1038m3; FDT 271m; Net 1.9m3/d","5284/G4: to recover 1733m3; FDT 1176m","5614/G6: to recover 13819m3; FDT 708m"],"tables":[{"rows":[["","Ave this week ( May 24th, m3/d)","Ave this week ( May 24th, m3/d)","Ave this week ( May 24th, m3/d)","Cum production in YTD,m3","Cum production in YTD,m3","Cum production in YTD,m3"],["","Budget","Actual","Actual -Budget","Budget","Actual","Actual - Budget"],["Existing well","919","904","-15","127,977","125,191","-2786"],["New non-thermal well","0","0","0","0","0","0"],["Polymer conversion","0","0","0","0","0","0"],["Reactivation+Stimulation","0","2","2","0","31","31"],["Thermal","124","87","-37","18,052","15,591","-2461"],["Total","1,043","993","-50","146,029","140,813","-5216"]]},{"rows":[["","","Oil Production m3/d","Oil Production m3/d","Variance"],["","","Last Week","This Week","+/- (m3/d)"],["Central","PF&WF","263.1","257.7","-5.4"],["North","PF","55.9","56.2","0.3"],["South","PF","118.2","121.8","3.6"],["EOR TOTAL","PF&WF","437.2","435.6","-1.5"]]},{"rows":[["ID","Brief Description"]]},{"rows":[["ID","Brief Description"]]},{"rows":[["Wells for Conversion","Injection well","PAD","Mixing Area","First Injection Date","Comments"]]},{"rows":[["Double rig and Single Rigs SS18/SS19","7 jobs completed by Double rig and Single Rigs SS18/SS19"],["Flush by Rig SS17","4 jobs completed by Flush by rig SS17"],["Rig less Jobs","2 wells/jobs - completed by Rig less"]]},{"rows":[["Type","Comment"],["Injector wells","1858S water flo