  ('7ed50135-1d72-5257-932f-d9ad8b55088a'::uuid, 'reservoir', 'approved'::entry_status, '{"source_file":"2026-06-07 Weekly Information Report (1).docx","report_label":"1-7 June 2026","starts_on":"2026-06-01","ends_on":"2026-06-07","department_id":"reservoir","paragraphs":["Double check all vertical wells which could lead to the flow of 5405-D1, the new information is that the cement interval of 599-S in the schematic is not correct; the actual top of cement is below D1. So it’s high risk one. Suggest monitoring wellhead pressure of both 599-S and 527b-S to get more useful data.","Completed the reactivation plan and stimulation of disposal plan to improve the production for the next step.","Start to make a comprehensive analysis of polymer flooding, in order to stable the production in the case without new drilling.","Actual Production Vs. 2026 Budget as of June 7th","not updated due to issue of database","Two polymer producers have weekly production incremental higher than 2m3/d.","Recovered after workover –5829.","Two polymer producers have weekly production loss equal/higher than 2 m3/d.","Gross decrease– 5808 and 5037-L3;","The average injection volume in the last week was 2378m3/d from 2342m3/d or 36m3/d more than the previous week. The main issues have been:","Instrument problems in J165 pumps at P28A and N31B have caused frequent stops. After this week''s interventions the injection was normalized.","VFD of J165 of O29A was used to O32B. The VFD of O32B get fixed by electricians and installed to O29A","Active injectors are 39. Average injection 60.9m3/day/injector. While 3 of the reactivates injectors remains SI to monitor pattern performance","PSU300 is running with 78%. PSU600 is running with 41% of capacity.","Av. daily polymer consumption of the week was 3.3 bags. Stocks in store are 121 bags (on 7 June)","The injection test in 5400/M pad N28B was conducted on June 6 and 7. No rig job in the well was performed except installation of safety valve on the wellhead.","The test was stopped after 26m³ injection of polymer solution 25cPs. Casing pressure reached sharply 1200psi causing leakage from the tubing rotator","Injector’s performance during the last week have been:","Rates and WHP have been stabilized in almost all the injectors","Fluctuation at 6108/M. After every stop the volume temporary dropped by 25%","There are signs of positive pressure at 6189/D3U. The rate dropped a bit","Under strict monitor the 4 self-producing WSW in G1 and G2 zone due to high reservoir energy. Max casing pressure at WSW 963/G1 remains at 150psi.","10 WSW are in production. Supplied the boiler #3 and small quantity of fresh water used for the dust control in the roads.","The installation of sunshade in all the flowmeters of fresh water sources has been completed","Hot water with Surfactant and Viscosity Reducer, Huff & Puff.","6002/M – to recover 432.3m3; FDT 171m; Net 3.6m3/d","5577/G4: to recover 1008m3; FDT 271m; Net 1.9m3/d","5284/G4: to recover 1733m3; FDT 1176m","5614/G6: to recover 13819m3; FDT 708m"],"tables":[{"rows":[["","Ave this week ( June 7th, m3/d)","Ave this week ( June 7th, m3/d)","Ave this week ( June 7th, m3/d)","Cum production in YTD,m3","Cum production in YTD,m3","Cum production in YTD,m3"],["","Budget","Actual","Actual -Budget","Budget","Actual","Actual - Budget"],["Existing well","910","921","11","140,768","139,344","-1424"],["New non-thermal well","0","0","0","0","0","0"],["Polymer conversion","0","0","0","0","0","0"],["Reactivation+Stimulation","2","3","1","20","67","47"],["Thermal","127","94","-33","19,806","15,591","-4215"],["Total","1,039","1,018","-21","160,594","155,002","-5592"]]},{"rows":[["","","Oil Production m3/d","Oil Production m3/d","Variance"],["","","Last Week","This Week","+/- (m3/d)"],["Central","PF&WF","236.6","239.4","2.8"],["North","PF","53.4","54.7","1.2"],["South","PF","89.6","92.4","2.8"],["EOR TOTAL","PF&WF","379.7","386.5","6.8"]]},{"rows":[["ID","Brief Description"]]},{"rows":[["ID","Bri