  ('2393b7f4-ec9b-5925-9030-38b81ffdd313'::uuid, 'geology', 'approved'::entry_status, '{"source_file":"2026-04-05 Weekly Information Report (1).docx","report_label":"30 March – 05 April 2026","starts_on":"2026-03-30","ends_on":"2026-04-05","department_id":"geology","paragraphs":[],"tables":[{"rows":[["PROJECT","PROJECT","CURRENT ACTIVITY/ISSUES"],["DEVELOPMENT DRILLING UPDATE","DEVELOPMENT DRILLING UPDATE","DEVELOPMENT DRILLING UPDATE","DEVELOPMENT DRILLING UPDATE"],["Active Drilling Update","Drilling Rig","Drilling Rig","Drilling Rig"],["Reservoir Study and Development Well Optimization","Basic study for oil field development 1.Gas Production and Geological Analysis Completed two presentations of gas production performance and geological characteristics of the G3, D, M0M, M1, and M2 layers to support gas potential evaluation. 2. Data Compilation and Analysis Compiled and organized sand data and single-well section for M-0M in wells 5005, 5006, and 5007 to support gas potential evaluation. 3. Geological Modeling – 5575-G3 well Area Completed geological model in 5575-G3 area and conducted a preliminary assessment of gas potential in the G3 reservoir. 4. Geological Modeling – 5992-M2 Well Area Completed geological model for 5992-M2 area and analyzed distribution of lateral section within M1 and M2 layers to provide a basis for reactivating the offset deviation wells. 5. Petrel Data Management and Interpretation Update Updated *.lic files for three wells in the Petrel project. Improved well log interpretation results for eight wells. New drilling Geological design Material for drilling","Basic study for oil field development 1.Gas Production and Geological Analysis Completed two presentations of gas production performance and geological characteristics of the G3, D, M0M, M1, and M2 layers to support gas potential evaluation. 2. Data Compilation and Analysis Compiled and organized sand data and single-well section for M-0M in wells 5005, 5006, and 5007 to support gas potential evaluation. 3. Geological Modeling – 5575-G3 well Area Completed geological model in 5575-G3 area and conducted a preliminary assessment of gas potential in the G3 reservoir. 4. Geological Modeling – 5992-M2 Well Area Completed geological model for 5992-M2 area and analyzed distribution of lateral section within M1 and M2 layers to provide a basis for reactivating the offset deviation wells. 5. Petrel Data Management and Interpretation Update Updated *.lic files for three wells in the Petrel project. Improved well log interpretation results for eight wells. New drilling Geological design Material for drilling","Basic study for oil field development 1.Gas Production and Geological Analysis Completed two presentations of gas production performance and geological characteristics of the G3, D, M0M, M1, and M2 layers to support gas potential evaluation. 2. Data Compilation and Analysis Compiled and organized sand data and single-well section for M-0M in wells 5005, 5006, and 5007 to support gas potential evaluation. 3. Geological Modeling – 5575-G3 well Area Completed geological model in 5575-G3 area and conducted a preliminary assessment of gas potential in the G3 reservoir. 4. Geological Modeling – 5992-M2 Well Area Completed geological model for 5992-M2 area and analyzed distribution of lateral section within M1 and M2 layers to provide a basis for reactivating the offset deviation wells. 5. Petrel Data Management and Interpretation Update Updated *.lic files for three wells in the Petrel project. Improved well log interpretation results for eight wells. New drilling Geological design Material for drilling"]]}],"subsections":[{"title":"GEOLOGY AND DEVELOPMENT","paragraphs":[],"tables":[{"rows":[["PROJECT","PROJECT","CURRENT ACTIVITY/ISSUES"],["DEVELOPMENT DRILLING UPDATE","DEVELOPMENT DRILLING UPDATE","DEVELOPMENT DRILLING UPDATE","DEVELOPMENT DRILLING UPDATE"],["Active Drilling Update","Drilling Rig","Drilling Rig","Drilling Rig"],["Reservoir Study and Develo