  ('533b9bc4-5caf-5732-b6e8-dec1b85b89d0'::uuid, 'geology', 'approved'::entry_status, '{"source_file":"2026-04-12 Weekly Information Report (1).docx","report_label":"06-12 April 2026","starts_on":"2026-04-06","ends_on":"2026-04-12","department_id":"geology","paragraphs":[],"tables":[{"rows":[["PROJECT","PROJECT","CURRENT ACTIVITY/ISSUES"],["DEVELOPMENT DRILLING UPDATE","DEVELOPMENT DRILLING UPDATE","DEVELOPMENT DRILLING UPDATE","DEVELOPMENT DRILLING UPDATE"],["Active Drilling Update","Drilling Rig","Drilling Rig","Drilling Rig"],["Reservoir Study and Development Well Optimization","Basic study for oil field development 1.M1–M2 Gas Potential Evaluation & Candidate Selection Delivered a comprehensive evaluation of gas potential in the M1 and M2 formations, identifying two candidate wells for gas testing through workovers (e.g., fishing and casing remediation). 2. Directional Well Reactivation Screening (5617-D3U Area) Completed the screening of reactivation opportunities for directional wells in the 5617-D3U area, providing a basis for potential production enhancement. 3.Reservoir Characterization for Well 6002 Assessed reservoir characteristics of well 6002, supporting decision-making for subsequent workover planning. 4. Petrel Workflow Development for Directional Well Extraction Established an automated Petrel workflow (26 lines) to efficiently extract directional well names across pads, improving data processing efficiency. 5. Well Data QA/QC and Depth Correction Enhanced data quality by updating perforation information for four wells and correcting raster log depth for one well. New drilling Geological design Material for drilling","Basic study for oil field development 1.M1–M2 Gas Potential Evaluation & Candidate Selection Delivered a comprehensive evaluation of gas potential in the M1 and M2 formations, identifying two candidate wells for gas testing through workovers (e.g., fishing and casing remediation). 2. Directional Well Reactivation Screening (5617-D3U Ar